sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as Usuário
  participant V as JSF View (index.xhtml)
  participant B as DropBean
  participant D as DropDAO
  participant EM as EntityManager
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  U->>V: Preenche título/conteúdo + Publicar
  V->>B: action salvar()
  B->>D: salvar(drop)
  D->>EM: begin()
  D->>EM: persist(drop)
  EM->>DB: INSERT drop
  DB-->>EM: OK
  D->>EM: commit()
  B-->>V: Atualiza lista
